data.description: Back on the market at no fault to the seller.  Escape the hustle and bustle of city life and immerse yourself in the beauty of the countryside.  This home is tucked away on almost 3 acres of shaded paradise.  Outside you’ll find a beautiful magnolia, persimmon, and oak tree, as well as several mature pecan trees.  There are also two outdoor buildings with electricity.  Inside you’ll find a cozy farmhouse style living space, and a large kitchen with butcher block countertops.  Fiber optic internet is available, so don’t feel like you’re missing out by living in the country.  Rest easy knowing that the appliances, condenser unit, and water heater are only a few years old!  Do you wish you could build another house close by?  Then this is a must!  The property is zoned to allow for a second dwelling to be built. This home is under $200,000 AND it is USDA eligible!  Schedule your appointment today and experience all the charm this home has to offer!
